{"tid":540432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"豐胸細腰！偽娘Coser緊身皮衣晒S型身材　網民：把那個東西藏哪？","createTime":"2018-01-25T13:02:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T07:16:21.000Z","uid":84436,"like":23,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"bc99466208ba3588b7e8164e7db81122c3862e7b","tid":540432,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T13:02:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1/152836/%E8%B1%90%E8%83%B8%E7%B4%B0%E8%85%B0-%E5%81%BD%E5%A8%98Coser%E7%B7%8A%E8%BA%AB%E7%9A%AE%E8%A1%A3%E6%99%92S%E5%9E%8B%E8%BA%AB%E6%9D%90-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E6%8A%8A%E9%82%A3%E5%80%8B%E6%9D%B1%E8%A5%BF%E8%97%8F%E5%93%AA-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1%2F152836%2F%25E8%25B1%2590%25E8%2583%25B8%25E7%25B4%25B0%25E8%2585%25B0-%25E5%2581%25BD%25E5%25A8%2598Coser%25E7%25B7%258A%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E7%259A%25AE%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E6%2599%2592S%25E5%259E%258B%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E6%259D%2590-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E6%258A%258A%25E9%2582%25A3%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259D%25B1%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E8%2597%258F%25E5%2593%25AA-&d=mBckM7UUbg0EyCBurPNnjjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=e2c12d07\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1/152836/%E8%B1%90%E8%83%B8%E7%B4%B0%E8%85%B0-%E5%81%BD%E5%A8%98Coser%E7%B7%8A%E8%BA%AB%E7%9A%AE%E8%A1%A3%E6%99%92S%E5%9E%8B%E8%BA%AB%E6%9D%90-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E6%8A%8A%E9%82%A3%E5%80%8B%E6%9D%B1%E8%A5%BF%E8%97%8F%E5%93%AA-</a><br />\n<br />\n熱愛角色扮演的Cosplayer（簡稱Coser），經常會度身訂造角色造型及道具，為求逼真，即使穿上緊身衣服後透不過氣來，仍要苦忍呈現最完美一面。廣州一名著名Coser，日前現身當地動漫活動時，穿着超緊身黑色皮製連身衣，展示其豐滿上圍、纖幼蛇腰及長腿，輕易成為全場焦點，但圍觀者卻萬萬想不到，經常戴面罩亮相的Coser竟然是男生！<br />\n<br />\n該名偽娘Coser名叫「知世無敵無敵無敵犀利」，不時在微博及Twitter上載性感的Cosplay照，雖然是男兒身，但身材打扮比許多女生還要火辣。除了今次以束孖辮、穿皮衣的造型搶鏡外，去年10月他參加動漫遊戲展時，曾Cosplay輕小說「無頭騎士異聞錄」中的角色「塞爾提」，他戴上黃色頭盔，身穿超緊連身皮衣及4吋高跟鞋，拿着黑色鐮刀，不停擺出拗腰、挺胸收腹等的撩人動作，吸引在場攝影師狂拍照，相關照片更一度在微博瘋傳，甚至令日本網民亦留意到，更將他列入「2018年一定會喜歡的人」排行榜。<br />\n<br />\n網民對這位偽娘Coser紛紛表示讚嘆，坦言被他的魔鬼身材吸引，亦有人提出疑問，「你把東西藏哪了？」、「為什麼有胸部？」。有女網民則埋怨「這麼細的腿和骨架，叫我們情何以堪？」。面對大家的疑問，「知世」曾透露自己豐滿的上圍，是靠矽膠Nude Bra裝出來的。"},{"pid":"5c04eb7ef8a19dbdaf3efd25a2969f3c1167448e","tid":540432,"uid":45368,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T13:03:15.000Z","msg":"YOU"},{"pid":"d90e7cd8638ef2bb327e79a8bb00179a1bd68267","tid":540432,"uid":50779,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T13:04:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48bcf1b36ce95edbef1ae7145be8febc107991ec","tid":540432,"uid":43042,"like":11,"dislike":42,"score":-31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T13:08:35.000Z","msg":"我們中國的最偉大最永久，而且最普遍的藝術也就是男人扮女人。"},{"pid":"b2bfe25530b1a5500634598df696bd5f401cee63","tid":540432,"uid":53568,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"48bcf1b36ce95edbef1ae7145be8febc107991ec","tid":540432,"uid":43042,"like":11,"dislike":42,"score":-31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T13:08:35.000Z","msg":"我們中國的最偉大最永久，而且最普遍的藝術也就是男人扮女人。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T13:13:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45364b710484955b09431f7a6564d9f056025888","tid":540432,"uid":33642,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T13:13:59.000Z","msg":"you竟然是個boy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c20242ca3e54ba72234df3fe5a5d6a470e9bdda2","tid":540432,"uid":62226,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T13:14:42.000Z","msg":"01<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2aaef40b63c60095b092c436db6206e7387cdd9","tid":540432,"uid":11046,"like":98,"dislike":2,"score":96,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T13:16:52.000